data.description: Beautiful Pace home with a new roof on a big lot!  Inside updates include granite kitchen countertops, several new kitchen appliances, paint and more.  Need space to entertain?  This home has what you're looking for: A formal dining room, enclosed Florida Room that's heated and cooled, and a living room with wood burning fireplace.  The large back yard has a wide covered patio, a firepit, and a new privacy fence was installed in 2022. Inside laundry has extra storage. Yard has a sprinkler system on a well and the home has a termite bond. Double garage, plus extra parking on the big driveway and concrete pad behind the double gate.  Seller to provide a one-year home warranty.  New 4 ton HVAC heat pump outdoor unit installed August '23.  Inside and out, this home is great!
